{"tid":810106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【被傳不忠】英前外相約翰遜發聲明 與結婚25年妻子離婚","createTime":"2018-09-07T16:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T04:27:38.000Z","uid":20924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d324ec2f9910b7776839c8cf4c2addea382d9fd","tid":810106,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"英國前外相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）周五宣佈已與妻子惠勒（Marina Wheeler）分居，並正辦理離婚。<br />\n<br />\n兩人發表的聯合聲明中表示，他們早前已經分居，並正開始辦理離婚手續。54歲的約翰遜與同齡的人權律師惠勒結婚25年，英國《太陽報》周五報道，約翰遜對妻子不忠。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜今年7月因反對首相文翠珊的脫歐計劃呈辭，而博彩公司亦將他捧為接替文翠珊出任首相的大熱門。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/英國《衞報》"},{"pid":"782327a5b51c947857cea4d4ccdda5ffb3c57545","tid":810106,"uid":61546,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"莊漢生呀"},{"pid":"7e4578ff0d077c0025e02df35828d85442fb6771","tid":810106,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:13:20.000Z","msg":"原來Boris Johnson 今年先54<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1a0eb63fe7f787b63c97df2d2a83f663c12fe8","tid":810106,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e4578ff0d077c0025e02df35828d85442fb6771","tid":810106,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:13:20.000Z","msg":"原來Boris Johnson 今年先54<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article13205282.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/0_EU-referendum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle13205282.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615b%2F0_EU-referendum.jpg&h=0941a051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢老母同齡嘅話keep得好好"},{"pid":"d4a74517e44b4af11393fc0fa10cf0dc6c6328ed","tid":810106,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"782327a5b51c947857cea4d4ccdda5ffb3c57545","tid":810106,"uid":61546,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,